Brutal honesty
{{ljcomm|brutal_honesty}} is a community on [[livejournal]] dedicated to the cause of allowing rape survivors, chronic masturbators, and attention whores an outlet for their deep, dark secrets and scathing confessions. Semi-annually (read: every other week) a picture post is had where all the uglies, lurkers, and e-popular members can ass kiss one another and vie for attention. 

